{"word":"G150 - αἰσχρός - aischrós - ahee-skhros' - Filthy","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">αἰσχρός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">aischrós</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ahee-skhros'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Filthy</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"இழிவான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"base, dishonorable"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From the same as <a href=\"#/G153 - αἰσχύνομαι - aischýnomai - ahee-skhoo'-nom-ahee/153\">G153</a>; <i>shameful</i>, that is, <i>base</i> (specifically <i>venal</i>): - filthy.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G150/150\">G150</a>, <a href=\"#/G151/151\">G151</a>, <a href=\"#/G152/152\">G152</a>, <a href=\"#/G153/153\">G153</a>, <a href=\"#/G1870/1870\">G1870</a>, <a href=\"#/G2617/2617\">G2617</a>"}]}